09_Transport_Layer_TCP_Analysis
Aim: Analyze TCP headers using Wireshark.
Procedure:
Open Wireshark and select a Wi-Fi interface.

Start packet capture.

Filter packets by source IP address (IPv4 → Source Address).

Analyze TCP protocol headers.
Result: Successfully analyzed TCP headers.
